
The Turn Report
---------------

The turn report consists of the following sections:

   Banner and summary reports
       The turn number, month, year, and season
       Game statistics and the player's rank in various categories
       How many NP's the player has, and when the next one will be received
       Entity numbers for new nobles to be formed
       Unit summary chart
       Stack location report
       Stack weight chart

   Report for the player entity
       Log of player entity commands executed
       List of any unclaimed items, such as the starting gold or stone

   Report for each character
       Log of what the character did during the month
       Character statistics and ratings

   Report for each location seen during the turn
       Log of what happened in the location
       End-of-turn view of everything in the location

   Any new lore sheets the player has learned

   Order template

Here is a sample set of orders a new player sent in, and the resulting
turn report.

begin 613 snausages

unit 2857 # Dr. F
   move in
   form 4611 "Joel Robinson"
   form 3386 "TV's Frank"
   study 125 # Construction
   move out
   recruit 10
   make 95 10

unit 3386 # Frank
   stack 2857
   claim 1 300
   study 129 # Mining
   make 95 10

unit 4611 # Joel
   claim 1 500
   form 3095 "Gypsy"
   study 126 # Alchemy
   make 95 10

unit 3095 # Gypsy
   stack 4611
   claim 1 100
   study 120 # Shipcraft
   make 95 10

end

