>   4611 cu26 2857 c500  100  0     400                     Joel Robinson
>                                  ==== ==== ==== ==== ====
>                                  1500    6               

This is a summary of the player's units.

	column    meaning
	------    -------
	unit      The character
	loc       Where the character is
	undr      What unit the character is stacked beneath
	loyal     The kind and level of loyalty.  Examples:

			c500	contract-500
			o1	oath-1
			f10	fear-10

	heal      The character's health.  100=perfect health, 0=dead.
	B         Combat behind status. 0=front line in battle, 9=rear.
	CA        Current Aura (for magicians).
	gold      Gold owned by the character.
        peas      Number of peasants owned.
        work      Number of workers owned.
        sail      Number of sailors owned.
        figh      Total number of fighters, including soldiers, pikemen,
                  archers, swordsmen, etc.

